inputs.input_text: A classic Italian pasta dish made with eggs, cheese, pancetta, and black pepper.    To make it, you cook the pancetta in a pan, then mix it with the pasta, eggs,    and cheese to create a creamy sauce. The dish is typically served with a sprinkle    of black pepper on top.
